SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Schedule::deleteObject Delete a network storage schedule
Overview Delete a network storage schedule. &ldquo;&lsquo;This cannot be undone.&rdquo;&rsquo; &ldquo;deleteObject&rdquo; returns Boolean &ldquo;true&rdquo; on successful deletion or &ldquo;false&rdquo; if it was unable to remove a schedule;
